#例題練習
import random

my = int(input("o.剪刀 1.石頭 2.布: "))
com = random.randint(0, 2)
trans = ["剪刀", "石頭", "布"]
print("我的:", trans[my])
print("電腦:", trans[com])

if my == (com + 1) % 3:
    print("Win")
elif com == (my + 1) % 3:
    print("Lose")
else:
    print("Even")
----------
1. 如果有隱藏的比較關係 -> 用整數(int)且從0開始

2. 如果要用別隻.py -> 要先引用(除了built-in function)
import .py名 / 照抄.
例如:
import random / random.randint(0, 2)
import a.b.c / a.b.c.z()

3. 清單(list)
list1 = ["xxx", "xxx", "xxx"]
           0      1      2
查詢(key-value)
key:0,1,2  value:"xxx","xxx","xxx"
查詢對象[key]

4. 有循環關係
13 / 3 = 4...2
a. 商: 25 // 3 -> 4
b. 餘: 25 %(mod) 3 -> 2

0 % 3 -> 0
1 % 3 -> 1
2 % 3 -> 2
3 % 3 -> 0
4 % 3 -> 1
5 % 3 -> 2
6 % 3 -> 0

0~n: % (n+1)
